title.narrative: Availability of adequate technical expertise to support the programme delivery and the office management.

description.narrative: Besides all the challenges experienced with numerous personnel changes (two P4s, one P3 and one NOB accepting new international assignments, and the replacements coming on board slowly during 2021) UNICEF Education Section could fill the gaps with the remaining staff and ensure that annual workplan deliverables were all achieved and support to partners and MoE regularly provided. Education staff at central and field level could ensure that educational services were provided to children, despite the challenging environment. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:16/01/2022
